description: Enjoy this spacious (1,966 SF) bi-level in the Thomas Park area of South Boston, conveniently located near Carson Beach, Moakley Park, and steps to the West Broadway shops & restaurants. Initially converted in 1999, the unit and exterior have recently undergone many upgrades/renovations, including siding, composite decking, a new HVAC furnace, new stainless steel appliances, refinished hardwood floors on the main level, and the unit was completely painted.This Seven room, four-bedroom unit with two full baths condo has an open floor plan on the main level, including a granite/stainless steel kitchen, a large dining area, a sun-filled living room with a gas fireplace, a home office/4th bedroom, and a full bath. The lower level, well above grade in the rear, has three large bedrooms and a full bath. You won't find a condo with better outdoor space - two large decks and a large fenced-in yard. This an excellent Investment unit!
